1
00:00:11,080 --> 00:00:12,039
(Xunzhou Prefecture)
Here she is.

2
00:00:12,240 --> 00:00:14,080
Lady Sanniang is coming.

3
00:00:15,240 --> 00:00:17,719
Sanniang.

4
00:00:19,079 --> 00:00:19,920
Sanniang.

5
00:00:20,399 --> 00:00:23,000
Sanniang, it's me.

6
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:24,160
(Seven years later)

7
00:00:24,160 --> 00:00:24,879
Sanniang.

8
00:00:25,079 --> 00:00:27,239
Lady Sanniang, do you remember me?

9
00:00:27,960 --> 00:00:28,600
Sanniang.

10
00:00:29,679 --> 00:00:31,519
Do you remember me?

11
00:00:31,719 --> 00:00:32,799
Sanniang, just ignore them.

12
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:33,759
Sanniang.

13
00:00:34,079 --> 00:00:35,520
Sanniang, look at me.

14
00:00:35,719 --> 00:00:37,600
Lady Sanniang, I'm Mr. Ge.

15
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:40,719
I've been admiring you.

16
00:00:41,640 --> 00:00:44,280
Sanniang, I'm here to see you.

17
00:00:44,439 --> 00:00:45,479
If I can see you,

18
00:00:45,600 --> 00:00:47,640
I'm willing to die.

19
00:00:48,159 --> 00:00:49,359
You've seen me now.

20
00:00:50,320 --> 00:00:52,359
Why don't you die now?

21
00:02:27,728 --> 00:02:32,784
=Faithful=
(Adapted from the novel "Faithful")

22
00:02:33,170 --> 00:02:36,888
=Episode 6, Chapter 3, Part 2=
(Liu Sanniang Seduces a Young Man)

23
00:02:37,522 --> 00:02:40,802
The lotus grows
in the middle of the pond.

24
00:02:41,601 --> 00:02:45,042
Its pink leaves
and green buds sway in the wind.

25
00:02:45,642 --> 00:02:48,482
The emerald stalk stands tall.

26
00:02:48,722 --> 00:02:50,281
(Gentle Breeze)

27
00:02:50,281 --> 00:02:54,202
The pond gets fragrant
in the moonlit night.

28
00:02:56,202 --> 00:02:56,762
Incredible!

29
00:02:57,561 --> 00:02:59,522
This peacock can understand poetry.

30
00:02:59,841 --> 00:03:01,001
I told you.

31
00:03:01,362 --> 00:03:03,762
The top courtesan
of Xunzhou owns this garden.

32
00:03:04,281 --> 00:03:07,082
This peacock is her treasure.

33
00:03:07,561 --> 00:03:09,001
It's not an ordinary creature.

34
00:03:10,001 --> 00:03:12,922
Why hasn't Lady Sanniang shown up yet?

35
00:03:13,322 --> 00:03:15,161
The Zheng family invited her last night.

36
00:03:15,401 --> 00:03:16,802
She didn't come back all night.

37
00:03:17,281 --> 00:03:20,962
She must have served that old man well.

38
00:03:25,042 --> 00:03:26,962
You are in high spirits.

39
00:03:27,362 --> 00:03:30,161
Sanniang, you've kept me waiting.

40
00:03:30,962 --> 00:03:33,721
You guys have something important to do?

41
00:03:36,242 --> 00:03:38,322
I'll make it up to you with a drink.

42
00:03:42,441 --> 00:03:43,522
Are you satisfied now?

43
00:03:43,762 --> 00:03:44,561
Sanniang.

44
00:03:45,082 --> 00:03:47,642
You're two hours late.

45
00:03:47,841 --> 00:03:48,601
Well,

46
00:03:49,281 --> 00:03:52,042
do you think a drink is enough?

47
00:03:55,922 --> 00:03:59,161
What else do you want, Mr. Sun?

48
00:03:59,322 --> 00:04:02,881
What are you up to tonight?

49
00:04:03,242 --> 00:04:06,161
Ms. Wang from Shihua House is available.

50
00:04:06,681 --> 00:04:09,362
How about I arrange her for you?

51
00:04:09,642 --> 00:04:10,642
Sanniang.

52
00:04:12,322 --> 00:04:14,242
I thought you were a peerless beauty.

53
00:04:15,362 --> 00:04:16,281
Turns out you're vulgar.

54
00:04:17,721 --> 00:04:19,481
May I have your name?

55
00:04:21,746 --> 00:04:24,027
You were so funny.

56
00:04:24,306 --> 00:04:26,947
You are only a courtesan.

57
00:04:27,226 --> 00:04:28,666
You don't deserve to know my name.

58
00:04:30,067 --> 00:04:31,746
A courtesan?

59
00:04:32,707 --> 00:04:33,907
So what?

60
00:04:35,387 --> 00:04:37,707
Men are born strong

61
00:04:38,027 --> 00:04:40,986
and go to the battlefield
to earn merit and fame.

62
00:04:41,306 --> 00:04:42,426
You can become heroes.

63
00:04:43,467 --> 00:04:46,027
Women are born with good looks

64
00:04:46,587 --> 00:04:49,986
and if we use our attractiveness,
we will be considered indecent.

65
00:04:50,587 --> 00:04:52,067
It's all given by nature.

66
00:04:53,587 --> 00:04:55,346
Who is nobler?

67
00:04:56,866 --> 00:04:58,467
If you despise me,

68
00:05:00,746 --> 00:05:02,267
I will disdain you too.

69
00:05:02,866 --> 00:05:03,587
You...

70
00:05:03,746 --> 00:05:05,306
Chan, see him out.

71
00:05:17,627 --> 00:05:18,507
Who are you?

72
00:05:20,226 --> 00:05:23,306
Do you remember me, Miss Liu?

73
00:05:23,827 --> 00:05:25,267
I don't know you.

74
00:05:25,546 --> 00:05:26,786
Report to the official now.

75
00:05:26,986 --> 00:05:27,507
Yes.

76
00:05:27,666 --> 00:05:28,546
Wait.

77
00:05:29,746 --> 00:05:31,387
Seven years ago, in Huaizhou Prefecture,

78
00:05:32,587 --> 00:05:34,467
there was a lady named Rulan.

79
00:05:35,346 --> 00:05:38,546
Do you remember her?

80
00:05:45,106 --> 00:05:46,226
Meng Wan.

81
00:05:48,467 --> 00:05:51,707
Is she Lin Rulan's close friend?

82
00:05:51,986 --> 00:05:54,067
Yes.

83
00:05:54,587 --> 00:05:58,507
How did you know her?

84
00:05:59,746 --> 00:06:01,507
That's a long story.

85
00:06:02,947 --> 00:06:04,226
I came here today

86
00:06:05,346 --> 00:06:07,226
to ask you a favor.

87
00:06:13,027 --> 00:06:14,067
You all may leave.

88
00:06:21,106 --> 00:06:22,027
What is it?

89
00:06:22,226 --> 00:06:24,986
Zhao Yin just arrived here.

90
00:06:25,267 --> 00:06:26,147
Do you know him?

91
00:06:28,067 --> 00:06:29,306
I have never heard of him.

92
00:06:29,746 --> 00:06:32,027
He's from a noble family in the capital.

93
00:06:32,226 --> 00:06:34,707
He likes to hang out in brothels.

94
00:06:35,707 --> 00:06:36,666
Everywhere he goes,

95
00:06:37,027 --> 00:06:39,467
the first thing he does is
to meet the famous courtesans.

96
00:06:40,226 --> 00:06:42,067
If you can win his favor,

97
00:06:42,786 --> 00:06:46,106
it will bring us one step closer
to bringing down Wu Lian.

98
00:06:51,147 --> 00:06:52,627
Why are all the women

99
00:06:53,907 --> 00:06:56,027
in this world so foolish?

100
00:06:56,426 --> 00:06:57,746
What do you mean by that?

101
00:06:58,226 --> 00:07:00,546
Lin Rulan is already dead.

102
00:07:01,666 --> 00:07:04,507
Even if you kill Wu Lian,
what good will it do?

103
00:07:05,627 --> 00:07:07,707
Go ask around in Huaizhou Prefecture.

104
00:07:08,306 --> 00:07:10,387
How many people still remember her?

105
00:07:11,106 --> 00:07:12,467
You fool.

106
00:07:12,827 --> 00:07:15,827
If you dig up the past,

107
00:07:16,106 --> 00:07:20,106
it will only tarnish her reputation.

108
00:07:20,467 --> 00:07:22,267
What's wrong with you?

109
00:07:22,746 --> 00:07:24,267
I'm trying to be nice.

110
00:07:24,707 --> 00:07:25,786
Who is a fool?

111
00:07:28,627 --> 00:07:30,467
The one

112
00:07:31,267 --> 00:07:32,627
who is angry now.

113
00:07:33,186 --> 00:07:34,106
Stop.

114
00:07:36,947 --> 00:07:38,147
I won't argue with you.

115
00:07:38,827 --> 00:07:40,027
Anything else?

116
00:07:42,306 --> 00:07:43,426
Meng Wan said

117
00:07:44,346 --> 00:07:47,106
if you're unwilling to help,
she won't force you.

118
00:07:48,467 --> 00:07:50,346
But she hopes
you can return to Huaizhou Prefecture.

119
00:07:50,666 --> 00:07:54,147
There's something
you'll be interested in.

120
00:07:57,266 --> 00:07:59,794
(Ning Mansion)

121
00:08:00,027 --> 00:08:01,387
I am Hu.

122
00:08:02,147 --> 00:08:07,067
I do a street fortune-telling business.

123
00:08:07,707 --> 00:08:08,907
I have nothing to do

124
00:08:09,947 --> 00:08:11,387
with that lame man.

125
00:08:11,666 --> 00:08:12,728
Well,

126
00:08:13,048 --> 00:08:15,507
did he buy banner from you?

127
00:08:15,947 --> 00:08:19,546
Yes, he also bought my copper bell

128
00:08:20,067 --> 00:08:21,707
and divination compass.

129
00:08:22,426 --> 00:08:23,666
Did he mention

130
00:08:24,267 --> 00:08:26,186
what he wanted to do with these items?

131
00:08:26,467 --> 00:08:28,426
He didn't.

132
00:08:35,627 --> 00:08:37,627
Alright, take him away.

133
00:08:38,066 --> 00:08:38,946
Yes.

134
00:08:46,907 --> 00:08:48,987
Madam, you heard him.

135
00:08:49,666 --> 00:08:52,306
That lame man is a cheater.

136
00:08:52,666 --> 00:08:55,186
I bet someone tried
to sow discord between us.

137
00:08:55,507 --> 00:08:57,786
You must not believe him.

138
00:09:00,306 --> 00:09:01,147
Mr. Wu.

139
00:09:02,107 --> 00:09:04,387
You're so omnipotent.

140
00:09:04,786 --> 00:09:06,107
Whoever comes to my mansion,

141
00:09:06,267 --> 00:09:07,227
and whatever they have said,

142
00:09:07,426 --> 00:09:08,627
you know it all.

143
00:09:09,546 --> 00:09:10,147
I...

144
00:09:10,186 --> 00:09:12,387
Alright, you may leave.

145
00:09:12,666 --> 00:09:14,066
We'll not talk about this for now.

146
00:09:14,466 --> 00:09:18,027
Are you satisfied about the sample
for the Her Majesty's birthday?

147
00:09:18,107 --> 00:09:19,706
Just put it aside.

148
00:09:20,066 --> 00:09:21,387
I need time to think about it.

149
00:09:24,227 --> 00:09:27,747
Madam, you still don't trust me?

150
00:09:29,027 --> 00:09:31,747
Didn't you hear me?
I told you to go back.

151
00:09:51,306 --> 00:09:53,306
It's mainly embroidered in a fine way.

152
00:09:53,786 --> 00:09:57,826
It includes mallow, daylily,
cereus, and other flowers.

153
00:10:00,706 --> 00:10:02,826
Too flashy and petty.

154
00:10:05,987 --> 00:10:08,066
This is a pair of mandarin ducks.

155
00:10:08,786 --> 00:10:10,507
A pair of mandarin ducks perch

156
00:10:10,747 --> 00:10:12,466
on the shore.

157
00:10:12,706 --> 00:10:13,546
It's meaningful.

158
00:10:13,706 --> 00:10:16,426
This is for a birthday, not a wedding.

159
00:10:16,826 --> 00:10:17,747
It's inappropriate.

160
00:10:19,826 --> 00:10:21,426
What about this one?

161
00:10:21,907 --> 00:10:25,747
It seems both solid and void.

162
00:10:30,306 --> 00:10:31,347
Where did this come from?

163
00:10:31,946 --> 00:10:34,347
It's from the Huangji Embroidery House.

164
00:10:34,867 --> 00:10:37,786
It's peculiar and unheard of.

165
00:10:40,306 --> 00:10:42,147
Are you unsatisfied?

166
00:10:42,466 --> 00:10:45,306
They really can't be compared
to Wu Lian's Yanyu Embroidery.

167
00:10:45,747 --> 00:10:46,586
Well...

168
00:10:49,507 --> 00:10:50,267
What?

169
00:10:50,666 --> 00:10:51,786
I misspoke last time.

170
00:10:52,186 --> 00:10:53,546
I dare not contradict you.

171
00:10:58,186 --> 00:10:58,747
Forget it.

172
00:11:00,107 --> 00:11:02,546
I'll check out Wu Lian's samples.

173
00:11:04,507 --> 00:11:05,466
Madame Xu.

174
00:11:06,107 --> 00:11:08,466
You accompany me to the Yanyu Tower.

175
00:11:10,426 --> 00:11:11,347
Yes.

176
00:11:15,474 --> 00:11:18,130
(Yanyu Tower)

177
00:11:26,107 --> 00:11:27,426
Greetings.

178
00:11:27,627 --> 00:11:29,586
I will immediately invite Mr. Wu over.

179
00:11:36,050 --> 00:11:38,002
(Yanyu Tower)

180
00:11:41,786 --> 00:11:42,546
Wan, come on.

181
00:11:42,627 --> 00:11:43,387
Slow down.

182
00:11:44,867 --> 00:11:45,666
Where are we going?

183
00:11:45,946 --> 00:11:47,706
A new girl has just arrived.

184
00:11:47,907 --> 00:11:49,186
She is begging to return.

185
00:11:49,387 --> 00:11:50,306
It's funny.

186
00:11:50,867 --> 00:11:52,186
Walk slowly.

187
00:12:05,507 --> 00:12:07,627
Get up, or we'll be scolded.

188
00:12:08,066 --> 00:12:08,907
Wan, look.

189
00:12:11,147 --> 00:12:13,227
That cloud looks like a little rabbit.

190
00:12:15,546 --> 00:12:16,507
Yes.

191
00:12:18,066 --> 00:12:20,466
Look at that one.

192
00:12:21,227 --> 00:12:22,267
It looks like a rabbit, right?

193
00:12:42,466 --> 00:12:44,507
What can I do for you?

194
00:12:45,387 --> 00:12:47,186
Show me

195
00:12:47,706 --> 00:12:49,186
your embroidery samples again.

196
00:12:50,706 --> 00:12:52,267
Sure, please follow me, Madam.

197
00:13:02,267 --> 00:13:03,306
What do you think?

198
00:13:04,826 --> 00:13:06,147
Mr. Wu is renowned,

199
00:13:06,426 --> 00:13:07,747
and his skill is unquestionable.

200
00:13:07,987 --> 00:13:09,306
It is truly unique.

201
00:13:10,387 --> 00:13:13,546
This must be Madame Xu.

202
00:13:14,987 --> 00:13:16,387
I heard about Mr. Wu

203
00:13:16,546 --> 00:13:19,267
from Manshu in Qizhou.

204
00:13:19,867 --> 00:13:20,747
When I see you today,

205
00:13:21,546 --> 00:13:24,306
I think you deserve your reputation.

206
00:13:24,867 --> 00:13:26,147
Madame Xu,

207
00:13:26,867 --> 00:13:28,186
you flatter me.

208
00:13:29,147 --> 00:13:30,227
In three more months,

209
00:13:30,426 --> 00:13:32,147
it will be
the Her Majesty's 70th birthday.

210
00:13:33,186 --> 00:13:36,107
Many gifts are almost ready.

211
00:13:37,066 --> 00:13:38,546
So, in the coming days,

212
00:13:39,066 --> 00:13:40,946
you will have to work hard.

213
00:13:42,306 --> 00:13:45,306
It is my honor to be able to help.

214
00:14:07,306 --> 00:14:08,107
Mr. Wu.

215
00:14:09,387 --> 00:14:11,227
There was once an embroideress here

216
00:14:11,546 --> 00:14:12,466
named Meng Wan.

217
00:14:12,907 --> 00:14:13,946
Do you still remember?

218
00:14:14,426 --> 00:14:18,706
There are dozens of embroideresses
studying here every year.

219
00:14:19,066 --> 00:14:20,387
I can't remember.

220
00:14:24,586 --> 00:14:25,907
She is from Huaizhou.

221
00:14:28,706 --> 00:14:30,706
But I can't remember

222
00:14:31,306 --> 00:14:32,546
her exact background.

223
00:14:34,507 --> 00:14:38,066
You find out where she is now.

224
00:14:38,186 --> 00:14:39,066
Yes.

225
00:15:02,987 --> 00:15:04,267
I have long heard of you.

226
00:15:05,107 --> 00:15:06,306
To be honest,

227
00:15:07,946 --> 00:15:09,267
you do look amazing.

228
00:15:13,507 --> 00:15:14,867
I have seen you once.

229
00:15:15,946 --> 00:15:16,946
When?

230
00:15:17,186 --> 00:15:18,107
Seven years ago.

231
00:15:19,347 --> 00:15:21,227
After Yamen held court
for the Rulan Case,

232
00:15:21,666 --> 00:15:23,747
I went to the pharmacy
to bid her farewell.

233
00:15:24,027 --> 00:15:25,546
I saw you
at the back door of the pharmacy.

234
00:15:26,066 --> 00:15:27,186
She drove you out.

235
00:15:27,706 --> 00:15:29,027
You seemed lost.

236
00:15:29,987 --> 00:15:30,987
You and I are the same.

237
00:15:32,946 --> 00:15:34,867
There are people
who wanted to protect us,

238
00:15:36,227 --> 00:15:38,227
but they had to bear a lot for us.

239
00:15:38,706 --> 00:15:40,027
What do you mean by that?

240
00:15:42,987 --> 00:15:44,586
Seven years have passed in a flash.

241
00:15:45,907 --> 00:15:47,666
How have you been these years?

242
00:15:47,987 --> 00:15:48,946
After I let go

243
00:15:49,987 --> 00:15:51,826
of some things,

244
00:15:53,107 --> 00:15:54,507
I live more freely.

245
00:15:54,987 --> 00:15:56,666
It seems that you have already decided

246
00:15:57,306 --> 00:15:58,946
not to get involved in this matter.

247
00:15:59,306 --> 00:16:01,666
Madame Xu, I know

248
00:16:02,666 --> 00:16:04,907
you want to seek justice
for your friend.

249
00:16:05,586 --> 00:16:07,027
But have you ever thought

250
00:16:07,426 --> 00:16:08,666
if there is anything in this world

251
00:16:08,946 --> 00:16:12,984
that makes us insulted,

252
00:16:12,984 --> 00:16:14,907
and that we cannot abandon,

253
00:16:15,706 --> 00:16:17,466
it must not be a good thing.

254
00:16:18,466 --> 00:16:19,666
You and I are both women.

255
00:16:20,907 --> 00:16:22,466
I sincerely advise you.

256
00:16:23,027 --> 00:16:24,267
Let it go.

257
00:16:25,586 --> 00:16:27,227
Stop getting caught up in the past.

258
00:16:27,786 --> 00:16:29,546
Let me tell you

259
00:16:30,426 --> 00:16:32,387
another old story I have heard recently.

260
00:16:33,186 --> 00:16:34,147
Seven years ago,

261
00:16:34,666 --> 00:16:37,027
a prestigious man in Huaizhou Prefecture

262
00:16:38,267 --> 00:16:39,786
kept a geisha.

263
00:16:40,426 --> 00:16:43,066
This geisha offended the powerful

264
00:16:43,466 --> 00:16:44,867
and fled overnight.

265
00:16:45,507 --> 00:16:46,627
Not long after,

266
00:16:47,907 --> 00:16:50,066
the man suffered a disaster.

267
00:16:50,946 --> 00:16:53,466
I don't know what torment he suffered.

268
00:16:53,946 --> 00:16:57,466
Not only did all his wealth
go up in smoke,

269
00:16:58,546 --> 00:17:00,507
but he became insane.

270
00:17:02,186 --> 00:17:05,226
He has been living
on the streets for seven years.

271
00:17:05,946 --> 00:17:07,466
I often help him.

272
00:17:08,907 --> 00:17:10,706
He is so down and out,

273
00:17:11,746 --> 00:17:13,827
but he is unwilling to be settled.

274
00:17:15,746 --> 00:17:16,827
Now,

275
00:17:19,026 --> 00:17:21,307
I'm afraid only you can persuade him.

276
00:17:21,587 --> 00:17:22,907
Sir, give me a bun, please.

277
00:17:23,147 --> 00:17:24,347
I'll exchange it with something.

278
00:17:24,666 --> 00:17:25,387
Get away from me.

279
