537
00:31:15,746 --> 00:31:17,547
to be shipped overseas to sell,

538
00:31:18,107 --> 00:31:20,186
every time a cargo ship leaves the port,

539
00:31:20,387 --> 00:31:22,986
they have to get
one official warrant from me.

540
00:31:24,107 --> 00:31:26,827
Do you know what this means?

541
00:31:28,587 --> 00:31:31,026
Zhao Yin is the Supervisor
of the Minzhou Foreign Trade Bureau.

542
00:31:32,067 --> 00:31:33,466
He's in charge of maritime trade.

543
00:31:34,026 --> 00:31:35,746
