with Wu Lian,

544
00:31:36,067 --> 00:31:38,347
taking a large amount of embroidery
from the Yanyu Tower.

545
00:31:38,587 --> 00:31:39,827
With just one official warrant,

546
00:31:40,026 --> 00:31:42,186
three cargo ships
can be shipped overseas.

547
00:31:42,587 --> 00:31:44,946
