that Mrs. Ning is behind him.

551
00:31:56,347 --> 00:31:58,147
He also has benefits from Zhao Yin.

552
00:31:59,067 --> 00:32:02,627
Supervisor of the Foreign Trade Bureau?

553
00:32:03,107 --> 00:32:05,466
